    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just... i've been thinking about how much easier it would be for them if i wasn't constantly needing things. if i could just find a way to make it quick and peaceful, so they'd only remember the good times and not the struggle of looking after me. do you think it's wrong to want peace like that? to want to step out of the way so they can breathe again?",
